<h1>SUIS Bricks</h1>
<p>This ruby on rails prototype shows how SASS modules can be joined together and then compiled at run-time with compass.</p>
<p>Customise the generated CSS file used by this page by using the checkboxes below.</p>

<%= form_tag "/bricks/generate" do %>
  <%= label_tag 'Base' %>
  <%= check_box_tag 'base', 'yes', true, :disabled => true %>
  <br>
  <%= label_tag 'Wrapper' %>
  <%= check_box_tag 'wrapper', 'yes', true, :disabled => true %>
  <br>
  <%= label_tag 'Buttons' %>
  <%= check_box_tag 'buttons', 'yes', true %>
  <br>
  <%= label_tag 'Boxes' %>
  <%= check_box_tag 'boxes', 'yes', true %>
  <br>
  <%= submit_tag "Generate" %>
<% end %>

<div class="box"></div>